      "content_html": "\u003ch2\u003eNavigation\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API\"\u003eUnreal Engine C++ API Reference\u003c/a\u003e \u003e \u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API/Plugins\"\u003ePlugins\u003c/a\u003e \u003e \u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API/Plugins/ControlRig\"\u003eControlRig\u003c/a\u003e \u003e \u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API/Plugins/ControlRig/Units\"\u003eUnits\u003c/a\u003e \u003e \u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API/Plugins/ControlRig/Units/Hierarchy\"\u003eHierarchy\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch2\u003eInheritance Hierarchy\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API/Plugins/RigVM/RigVMCore/FRigVMStruct\"\u003eFRigVMStruct\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API/Plugins/ControlRig/Units/FRigUnit\"\u003eFRigUnit\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eFRigUnit_GetBoneTransform\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\u003ch2\u003eReferences\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003ctable\u003e\n  \u003cthead\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003cth\u003e \u003c/th\u003e\n      \u003cth\u003e \u003c/th\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n  \u003c/thead\u003e\n  \u003ctbody\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eModule\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API/Plugins/ControlRig\"\u003eControlRig\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eHeader\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e/Engine/Plugins/Animation/ControlRig/Source/ControlRig/Public/Units/Hierarchy/RigUnit_GetBoneTransform.h\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eInclude\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e#include \"Units/Hierarchy/RigUnit_GetBoneTransform.h\"\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n  \u003c/tbody\u003e\n\u003c/table\u003e\n\n\u003ch2\u003eSyntax\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cpre\u003e\u003ccode\u003eUSTRUCT \u0026#40;  \n\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;Meta\u0026#61;\u0026#40;DisplayName\u0026#61;\u0026quot;Get Transform\u0026quot;, Category\u0026#61;\u0026quot;Hierarchy\u0026quot;, DocumentationPolicy\u0026#61;\u0026quot;Strict\u0026quot;, Keywords\u0026#61;\u0026quot;GetBoneTransform\u0026quot;, Varying, Deprecated\u0026#61;\u0026quot;4.25\u0026quot;\u0026#41;\u0026#41;  \nstruct FRigUnit_GetBoneTransform : public FRigUnit  \n\u003c/code\u003e\u003c/pre\u003e\n\n\u003ch2\u003eRemarks\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eGetBoneTransform is used to retrieve a single transform from a hierarchy.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch2\u003eVariables\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003ctable\u003e\n  \u003cthead\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003cth\u003e \u003c/th\u003e\n      \u003cth\u003eType\u003c/th\u003e\n      \u003cth\u003eName\u003c/th\u003e\n      \u003cth\u003eDescription\u003c/th\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n  \u003c/thead\u003e\n  \u003ctbody\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/26128f6c-9c1a-4521-b11d-55d1b978ad75/api_variable_public.png\" alt=\"Public variable\" loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Public variable\" convert=\"false\" width=\"18\" /\u003e \u003cimg src=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/1a2a84dc-2230-4763-a0fd-988f9d7337f1/api_variable_meta.png\" alt=\"UProperty\" loading=\"lazy\" title=\"UProperty\" convert=\"false\" width=\"18\" /\u003e \u003cimg src=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/28130b26-e36c-4aa8-9488-3e28f8c50b62/api_variable_meta_serialization.png\" alt=\"Transient\" loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Transient\" convert=\"false\" width=\"18\" /\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003ebool\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003ebFirstUpdate\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eUsed to force first update to return initial pose.\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/18158a02-c69e-4cc6-8959-9b67887c5a20/api_variable_public.png\" alt=\"Public variable\" loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Public variable\" convert=\"false\" width=\"18\" /\u003e \u003cimg src=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/8270626a-901e-446f-8fed-f02f289a48cd/api_variable_meta.png\" alt=\"UProperty\" loading=\"lazy\" title=\"UProperty\" convert=\"false\" width=\"18\" /\u003e \u003cimg src=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/3ce569b2-fec6-4704-8027-aaceb72fb2b3/api_variable_meta_editor.png\" alt=\"Meta\" loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Meta\" convert=\"false\" width=\"18\" /\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API/Runtime/Core/UObject/FName\"\u003eFName\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eBone\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eThe name of the Bone to retrieve the transform for.\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/b1ee0d3b-601c-4742-bb3b-995f5d3d2a60/api_variable_public.png\" alt=\"Public variable\" loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Public variable\" convert=\"false\" width=\"18\" /\u003e \u003cimg src=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/46e1be56-ed95-4db3-a2ae-c38178c137d9/api_variable_meta.png\" alt=\"UProperty\" loading=\"lazy\" title=\"UProperty\" convert=\"false\" width=\"18\" /\u003e \u003cimg src=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/195ad0c6-b1b8-4485-88c2-0233ee1751d0/api_variable_meta_serialization.png\" alt=\"Transient\" loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Transient\" convert=\"false\" width=\"18\" /\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API/Plugins/ControlRig/Rigs/FCachedRigElement\"\u003eFCachedRigElement\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eCachedBone\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eUsed to cache the internally used bone index.\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/ea665878-bbaf-42c2-a43e-20d4a38e8958/api_variable_public.png\" alt=\"Public variable\" loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Public variable\" convert=\"false\" width=\"18\" /\u003e \u003cimg src=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/382ad560-4df7-44bc-b966-ab160b8ab864/api_variable_meta.png\" alt=\"UProperty\" loading=\"lazy\" title=\"UProperty\" convert=\"false\" width=\"18\" /\u003e \u003cimg src=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/471c113f-8737-4819-83e3-4dedf2efc1c3/api_variable_meta_editor.png\" alt=\"Meta\" loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Meta\" convert=\"false\" width=\"18\" /\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API/Plugins/RigVM/RigVMFunctions/ERigVMTransformSpace\"\u003eERigVMTransformSpace\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eSpace\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eDefines if the bone's transform should be retrieved in local or global space.\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/a623edd4-7c3a-4858-88d3-9676a2a685c3/api_variable_public.png\" alt=\"Public variable\" loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Public variable\" convert=\"false\" width=\"18\" /\u003e \u003cimg src=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/a8834ac3-a955-4d01-a43c-891de7265139/api_variable_meta.png\" alt=\"UProperty\" loading=\"lazy\" title=\"UProperty\" convert=\"false\" width=\"18\" /\u003e \u003cimg src=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/f355d579-dda8-4cef-8671-c64f515720b1/api_variable_meta_editor.png\" alt=\"Meta\" loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Meta\" convert=\"false\" width=\"18\" /\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API/Runtime/Core/Math/FTransform\"\u003eFTransform\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eTransform\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eThe current transform of the given bone - or identity in case it wasn't found.\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n  \u003c/tbody\u003e\n\u003c/table\u003e\n\n\u003ch2\u003eConstructors\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\u003ctable\u003e\n  \u003cthead\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003cth\u003e \u003c/th\u003e\n      \u003cth\u003eType\u003c/th\u003e\n      \u003cth\u003eName\u003c/th\u003e\n      \u003cth\u003eDescription\u003c/th\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n  \u003c/thead\u003e\n  \u003ctbody\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://d1iv7db44yhgxn.cloudfront.net/documentation/images/bbed2f79-71e4-4430-aa05-9fcde77ffd8a/api_function_public.png\" alt=\"Public function\" loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Public function\" convert=\"false\" width=\"18\" /\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e \u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/API/Plugins/ControlRig/Units/Hierarchy/FRigUnit_GetBoneTransform/__ctor\"\u003eFRigUnit_GetBoneTransform\u003c/a\u003e ()\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003e \u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n  \u003c/tbody\u003e\n\u003c/table\u003e\n\n\u003ch2\u003eOverridden from FRigVMStruct\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\u003ctable\u003e\n  \u003cthead\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003cth\u003e \u003c/th\u003